item.description:
Your server that contains the mirrored databases does not need a license if...&lt;br /&gt;
1. It only has mirrored databases on it - e.g. none that can be accessed directly.&lt;br /&gt;
2. If you fail over to it you may use it for a maximum of 30 days before you require a license.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Hope that helps.&lt;br /&gt;

